xt-white tracking-tight\">Planner UC</span><p class=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 leading-none\">Sistema de Gestión Académica</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-5\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-pink-300\">Universidad Continental</p><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white leading-snug\">Recupera el acceso<br/><span class=\"text-pink-200\">a tu cuenta.</span></h2><p class=\"text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed\">Sigue los pasos para verificar tu identidad y establecer una nueva contraseña segura para tu cuenta institucional.</p><div class=\"space-y-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-xs font-bold\" style=\"background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg></div><span class=\"text-sm\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45)\">Ingresa tu correo institucional</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-xs font-bold\" style=\"background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-key-round h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.586 17.414A2 2 0 0 0 2 18.828V21a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h3a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-1a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h1a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-1a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h.172a2 2 0 0 0 1.414-.586l.814-.814a6.5 6.5 0 1 0-4-4z\"></path><circle cx=\"16.5\" cy=\"7.5\" r=\".5\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></svg></div><span class=\"text-sm\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45)\">Verifica el código enviado</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-xs font-bold\" style=\"background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lock h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"11\" x=\"3\" y=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-sm\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45)\">Establece una nueva contraseña</span></div></div></div><p class=\"text-xs text-white/25\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> <!-- -->Planner UC — Universidad Continental</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col justify-between bg-white px-10 py-10\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-800 transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-left h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m12 19-7-7 7-7\"></path><path d=\"M19 12H5\"></path></svg>Volver al inicio de sesión</button><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><div class=\"h-1.5 rounded-full transition-all\" style=\"width:24px;background-color:#6B21A8\"></div><div class=\"h-1.5 rounded-full transition-all\" style=\"width:8px;background-color:#E5E7EB\"></div><div class=\"h-1.5 rounded-full transition-all\" style=\"width:8px;background-color:#E5E7EB\"></div></div></div><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w